(its a bit long but do read it! i put in alot of effort for this well thought of response:))
hello C: as someone who has watched jianhaotan videos since secondary school till now (almost finishing jc), i think that its pretty heartwarming to see how jianhaotan built a company with such dedicated employees who are willing to give back to the company! :)
Hence, my pick for the best team would be the production team! production is definitely a vital aspect of aNY youtube channel because the quality of the videos can help the viewer to have a very positive. perception of the channel. The production team even bought a G master lens, even teaming up just to buy that. This clearly shows the amount of commendable dedication they have towards their work. Viewers like myself do prefer videos of extremely high video quality. Hence to this effect, the reception of videos produced under Team Titan would perhaps, exponentially increase. This means growth for not only the Jianhao tan channel, but other channels such as Trevmonki and Ladies First, etc. Overall, improving the youtube experience in all the different channels. In esscence, the production team made the best investment with the money used, to help grow the company:)
